## Overview

Create the managed PostgreSQL (or MySQL) cluster in DigitalOcean.

---

## Tasks

### 4.1 Create Database Cluster

```bash
doctl databases create {{APP_NAME}}-postgres \
  --engine pg \
  --version 16 \
  --region {{REGION}} \
  --size db-s-1vcpu-2gb \
  --num-nodes 1
```

- [ ] Cluster created
- [ ] Capture cluster ID: `DB_ID=`

### 4.2 Wait for Cluster

```bash
# Check status
doctl databases list --format ID,Name,Status
```

- [ ] Status: online

